cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a method for unsupervised domain adaptation for image classification tasks. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also uses adversarial training, which is a common technique in machine learning and falls under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with image datasets, which could also place it under the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
